  "content": "<p data-pid=\"n1XDE25H\">问题可大了，上了四年大学，反而还能力退化了。这种大学教育，真是毁人不倦啊。在我看来，大学最重要的就是那张 jpg 了（学位证书），除此之外，不如自学（医学等实践成本很高的专业除外）。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-33669b0fb144a80b06ac7aecf2b3c1ef_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-rawwidth=\"828\" data-rawheight=\"1582\" data-size=\"normal\" data-caption=\"\" data-original-token=\"v2-33669b0fb144a80b06ac7aecf2b3c1ef\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-0e17e7c732257fee61c87d51cb21bcce_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"828\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-33669b0fb144a80b06ac7aecf2b3c1ef_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;828&#39; height=&#39;1582&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-rawwidth=\"828\" data-rawheight=\"1582\" data-size=\"normal\" data-caption=\"\" data-original-token=\"v2-33669b0fb144a80b06ac7aecf2b3c1ef\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-0e17e7c732257fee61c87d51cb21bcce_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"828\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-33669b0fb144a80b06ac7aecf2b3c1ef_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-33669b0fb144a80b06ac7aecf2b3c1ef_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p class=\"ztext-empty-paragraph\"><br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-2d84bfa75f8c4264f16502935d7590d8_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-rawwidth=\"828\" data-rawheight=\"1526\" data-size=\"normal\" data-caption=\"\" data-original-token=\"v2-2d84bfa75f8c4264f16502935d7590d8\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-76d3a897de41d5bef5453ddfaf6f05b9_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"828\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-2d84bfa75f8c4264f16502935d7590d8_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><i